OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,FPresident Donald Trump and other top
OL,7,FWhite House officials were evacuated
OL,8,Ffrom an annual dinner of the White
OL,9,FHouse Correspondents' Association
OL,10,Fafter a man armed with guns and knives
OL,11,Fstormed the lobby and opened fire.
OL,13,FHere's everything we know so far.
OL,15,FWhen did it happen?
OL,17,FGunshots were first heard at the White
OL,18,FHouse Correspondents Dinner at around
OL,19,F8.30pm on Saturday night, which is
OL,20,F1.30am BST.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
