OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,FWho was at the dinner?
OL,8,FPresident Donald Trump and First Lady
OL,9,FMelania Trump were both in attendance,
OL,10,Falong with Vice President JD Vance. It
OL,11,Fis rare to have both the president and
OL,12,Fhis vice president at the same event
OL,13,Ffor security reasons.
OL,15,FFBI director Kash Patel and US Defence
OL,16,FSecretary Pete Hegseth were also there.
OL,18,FThe event is typically attended by
OL,19,Fjournalists and other dignitaries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
