OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning
OL,11,FWho was the gunman?
OL,13,FThe shooting suspect was taken into
OL,14,Fcustody and identified as Cole Tomas
OL,15,FAllen, 31, from Torrance, California,
OL,16,Flaw enforcement officials said.
OL,18,FHe worked as a teacher and a video
OL,19,Fgame developer, according to reports
OL,20,Fby ITV News' US partner CNN.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
