OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,FWhat was his motive?
OL,8,FA motive was not immediately known,
OL,9,Fand acting Attorney General Todd
OL,10,FBlanche said charges related to
OL,11,FSaturday night's attack will be given
OL,12,Fsoon.
OL,14,FTrump described the man as "a lone
OL,15,Fwolf whack job" in a post on Truth
OL,16,FSocial, where he also posted a picture
OL,17,Fof the alleged assailant.
OL,19,FWas anybody injured?
