OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,FOne officer, who was shot but
OL,7,Fprotected by his bulletproof vest, was
OL,8,Ftaken to hospital and has since been
OL,9,Freleased, according to USSS Chief of
OL,10,FCommunications Anthony Guglielmi.
OL,12,FHe said the ballistic vest the agent
OL,13,Fwas wearing "helped us avoid a
OL,14,Fpotential tragedy," according to
OL,15,Freports by CNN.
OL,17,FNobody else is thought to have been
OL,18,Fharmed.
OL,20,FWhat has the president said?
OL,26,@uD@MOUvD@SO]
