OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,FThe US president gave a press
OL,7,Fconference shortly after the incident.
OL,9,FTrump said he thought it was a tray
OL,10,Fthat clattered on the ground when the
OL,11,Fsuspect charged the White House
OL,12,FCorrespondent's Dinner, adding that he
OL,13,Fand Melania were "whisked away"
OL,14,Fwithout much time to think.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@_O]
