OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,F"When you're impactful, they go after
OL,7,Fyou. When you're not impactful, they
OL,8,Fleave you alone," Trump, safe and
OL,9,Funinjured and still in his tuxedo,
OL,10,Fsaid at the White House two hours
OL,11,Flater. "They seem to think he was a
OL,12,Flone wolf."
OL,14,FHe had also wanted the dinner to
OL,15,Fcontinue despite what had happened.
OL,17,F"We wanted to stay tonight," Trump
OL,18,Fsaid. "I fought like hell to stay."
