OL,3,CShots fired at Trump dinner:
OL,4,CEverything we know so far
OL,6,F"This was an event dedicated to
OL,7,Ffreedom of speech that was supposed to
OL,8,Fbring together members of both parties
OL,9,Fwith members of the press. And in a
OL,10,Fcertain way, it did," the president
OL,11,Fadded.
